{"metadata":{"modules":[{"name":"PushwooshCore"}],"symbolKind":"method","roleHeading":"Type Method","fragments":[{"kind":"text","text":"+ "},{"text":"setReverseProxy:headers:","kind":"identifier"}],"role":"symbol","navigatorTitle":[{"text":"setReverseProxy:headers:","kind":"identifier"}],"title":"setReverseProxy:headers:","externalID":"c:objc(pl)PWConfiguration(cm)setReverseProxy:headers:"},"variants":[{"traits":[{"interfaceLanguage":"occ"}],"paths":["\/documentation\/pushwooshcore\/pwconfiguration\/setreverseproxy:headers:"]}],"schemaVersion":{"minor":3,"major":0,"patch":0},"sections":[],"identifier":{"url":"doc:\/\/com.pushwoosh.PushwooshCore\/documentation\/PushwooshCore\/PWConfiguration\/setReverseProxy:headers:","interfaceLanguage":"occ"},"primaryContentSections":[{"kind":"declarations","declarations":[{"platforms":["iOS"],"tokens":[{"kind":"text","text":"+ ("},{"preciseIdentifier":"c:v","kind":"typeIdentifier","text":"void"},{"kind":"text","text":") "},{"kind":"identifier","text":"setReverseProxy:"},{"kind":"text","text":"("},{"text":"NSString","preciseIdentifier":"c:objc(cs)NSString","kind":"typeIdentifier"},{"kind":"text","text":" *) "},{"text":"url","kind":"internalParam"},{"text":" ","kind":"text"},{"text":"headers:","kind":"identifier"},{"kind":"text","text":"("},{"kind":"typeIdentifier","text":"NSDictionary<NSString *,NSString *>","preciseIdentifier":"c:Q$objc(cs)NSDictionary"},{"text":" *) ","kind":"text"},{"text":"headers","kind":"internalParam"},{"kind":"text","text":";"}],"languages":["occ"]}]},{"kind":"parameters","parameters":[{"content":[{"inlineContent":[{"text":"The full URL of your reverse proxy endpoint (e.g., “https:\/\/proxy.company.com\/pushwoosh”). Must not be nil or empty.","type":"text"}],"type":"paragraph"}],"name":"url"},{"name":"headers","content":[{"inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"Optional dictionary of custom HTTP headers. Pass nil if no custom headers are needed."}],"type":"paragraph"}]}]},{"content":[{"level":2,"type":"heading","anchor":"discussion","text":"Discussion"},{"inlineContent":[{"text":"Routes all Pushwoosh SDK network requests through your own proxy server.","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"This is useful for:","type":"text"}],"type":"paragraph"},{"type":"unorderedList","items":[{"content":[{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"strong","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"Enterprise security"}]},{"text":": Route traffic through corporate proxies","type":"text"}]}]},{"content":[{"inlineContent":[{"type":"strong","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"Regional compliance"}]},{"text":": Ensure data flows through specific regions","type":"text"}],"type":"paragraph"}]},{"content":[{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"inlineContent":[{"text":"Network monitoring","type":"text"}],"type":"strong"},{"type":"text","text":": Inspect and log SDK traffic"}]}]},{"content":[{"inlineContent":[{"type":"strong","inlineContent":[{"text":"Firewall restrictions","type":"text"}]},{"text":": Work around corporate firewall rules","type":"text"}],"type":"paragraph"}]}]},{"inlineContent":[{"text":"The proxy must forward requests to the appropriate Pushwoosh API endpoints","type":"text"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"while preserving all headers and request body content."}],"type":"paragraph"},{"inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"Settings are not persisted and must be set on every app start."},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"type":"text","text":"URL must start with https:\/\/ or http:\/\/."},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"text":"Custom headers are only applied when reverse proxy is active.","type":"text"}],"type":"paragraph"},{"level":2,"anchor":"Example","text":"Example","type":"heading"},{"inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"Configure proxy for enterprise deployment:"}],"type":"paragraph"},{"type":"codeListing","code":["class NetworkConfiguration {","","    func configureForEnterprise() {","        guard let proxyURL = Configuration.shared.pushwooshProxyURL else {","            return","        }","","        Pushwoosh.configure.setReverseProxy(proxyURL, headers: nil)","","        Logger.info(\"Pushwoosh configured to use proxy: \\(proxyURL)\")","    }","","    func configureForRegion(_ region: Region) {","        switch region {","        case .eu:","            Pushwoosh.configure.setReverseProxy(","                \"https:\/\/eu-proxy.company.com\/pushwoosh\",","                headers: [\"X-Auth-Token\": \"your-token\"]","            )","        case .asia:","            Pushwoosh.configure.setReverseProxy(","                \"https:\/\/asia-proxy.company.com\/pushwoosh\",","                headers: nil","            )","        case .us:","            break \/\/ No proxy needed","        }","    }","}"],"syntax":"swift"}],"kind":"content"}],"kind":"symbol","hierarchy":{"paths":[["doc:\/\/com.pushwoosh.PushwooshCore\/documentation\/PushwooshCore","doc:\/\/com.pushwoosh.PushwooshCore\/documentation\/PushwooshCore\/PWConfiguration"]]},"abstract":[{"text":"Sets a reverse proxy URL and optional custom HTTP headers for all SDK network requests.","type":"text"}],"references":{"doc://com.pushwoosh.PushwooshCore/documentation/PushwooshCore/PWConfiguration":{"type":"topic","identifier":"doc:\/\/com.pushwoosh.PushwooshCore\/documentation\/PushwooshCore\/PWConfiguration","kind":"symbol","title":"PWConfiguration","url":"\/documentation\/pushwooshcore\/pwconfiguration","fragments":[{"kind":"identifier","text":"PWConfiguration"}],"role":"symbol","abstract":[]},"doc://com.pushwoosh.PushwooshCore/documentation/PushwooshCore/PWConfiguration/setReverseProxy:headers:":{"abstract":[{"text":"Sets a reverse proxy URL and optional custom HTTP headers for all SDK network requests.","type":"text"}],"identifier":"doc:\/\/com.pushwoosh.PushwooshCore\/documentation\/PushwooshCore\/PWConfiguration\/setReverseProxy:headers:","fragments":[{"text":"+ ","kind":"text"},{"text":"setReverseProxy:headers:","kind":"identifier"}],"url":"\/documentation\/pushwooshcore\/pwconfiguration\/setreverseproxy:headers:","role":"symbol","navigatorTitle":[{"text":"setReverseProxy:headers:","kind":"identifier"}],"type":"topic","kind":"symbol","title":"setReverseProxy:headers:"},"doc://com.pushwoosh.PushwooshCore/documentation/PushwooshCore":{"url":"\/documentation\/pushwooshcore","identifier":"doc:\/\/com.pushwoosh.PushwooshCore\/documentation\/PushwooshCore","type":"topic","title":"PushwooshCore","role":"collection","abstract":[{"text":"Core foundation module for Pushwoosh SDK.","type":"text"}],"kind":"symbol"}}}